==English==

===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|cmn|-}} {{zh-l|湖南}}, literally “south of the lake”, referring to Lake Dongting.

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}
{{wikipedia}}

# A province of the [[People's Republic of China]], located in the middle reaches of the Yangtze River and south of Lake Dongting.

